Up we go, up we go.

55
00:02:22,475 --> 00:02:23,309
Alright, gotcha.

56
00:02:25,436 --> 00:02:26,271
Come on.

57
00:02:26,354 --> 00:02:27,897
My name is Wendy Akiyama.

58
00:02:27,981 --> 00:02:29,524
And I'm Ron Akiyama.

59
00:02:29,983 --> 00:02:33,278
